b15d514517b55f4660f4eaa84330bd0","type":"0","type_desc":null,"type_icon":null,"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=47%E5%A4%A924%E8%BD%A6%E5%86%BB%E8%B4%A7%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E9%98%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%A3%E5%B9%B6%E6%8B%8D%E5%8D%96&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"rank":9,"title":"女孩高考查分超预期 老师跳起拥抱","desc":"6月23日，内蒙古巴彦淖尔市衡越实验中学一女孩高考查分获538分，比预期超出38分。老师当场跳起与学生紧紧相拥。","score":"7043921","score_desc":"704.39w","cover":"https://fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com/hotboard_image/38b45a9e1d40ad202ec7f92fa1bebfa4","type":"0","type_desc":null,"type_icon":null,"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%9F%A5%E5%88%86%E8%B6%85%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F+%E8%80%81%E5%B8%88%E8%B7%B3%E8%B5%B7%E6%8B%A5%E6%8A%B1&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"rank":10,"title":"世界杯：哥伦比亚VS刚果金","desc":"6月24日10:00，2026美加墨世界杯小组赛K组第二轮哥伦比亚vs刚果民主共和国。","score":"6944140","score_desc":"694.41w","cover":"https://fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com/hotboard_image/b336db563fed85297bdf62fa30da405d","type":"1","type_desc":"新","type_icon":"https://search-operate.cdn.bcebos.com/42e626c5469cc4cd3b91131bcfe53d44.png","url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9D%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%93%A5%E4%BC%A6%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9AVS%E5%88%9A%E6%9E%9C%E9%87%91&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"rank":11,"title":"一盘蚊香=几十支烟？专家辟谣","desc":"网传“一盘蚊香等于几十支烟”不实，专家指出，蚊香与香烟的成分、作用方式不同，呼吸道影响因人而异，日常使用蚊香要保持空气流通。","score":"6851678","score_desc":"685.17w","cover":"https://fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com/hotboard_image/385ead8061876088b525f056f625c944","type":"0","type_desc":null,"type_icon":null,"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%98%E8%9A%8A%E9%A6%99%3D%E5%87%A0%E5%8D%81%E6%94%AF%E7%83%9F%EF%BC%9F%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"rank":12,"title":"看台强吻夏奇拉的是她儿子","desc":"6月23日，夏奇拉带13岁长子米兰观看世界杯时，因米兰身高近1.78米且戴帽遮挡面容，其亲吻母亲的动作被全球观众误认为“新男友强吻”，后证实为亲子互动。","score":"6756381","score_desc":"675.64w","cover":"https://fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com/hotboard_image/91ce3df92bf4e3986135c78cd4de20d1","type":"0","type_desc":null,"type_icon":null,"u